     <h2><font color="#000080"><!-- 2004-09-02 -->
	 
	 Friday Cat Photo: Maple Snell
	 </font>
     </h2>
    

	<p>
    <div style="clear:both;"></div><div style="padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; float: none; padding-top: 0px" id="scid:0767317B-992E-4b12-91E0-4F059A8CECA8:915e90d6-b9ce-4d9a-b773-b4197757a4c2" class="wlWriterEditableSmartContent">Technorati Tags: <a href="http://technorati.com/tags/cats" rel="tag">cats</a>, <a href="http://technorati.com/tags/Friday+cat+pictures" rel="tag">Friday cat pictures</a>, <a href="http://technorati.com/tags/Maple+Snell" rel="tag">Maple Snell</a>, <a href="http://technorati.com/tags/Jamie+Snell" rel="tag">Jamie Snell</a>, <a href="http://technorati.com/tags/Sara+Snell" rel="tag">Sara Snell</a></div> <p><a title="Maple Snell, the cat (click for larger image)" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/orcmid/3259668702/sizes/l/" target="_blank"><img style="margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; float: none" title="Maple Snell, the Friday Cat (click for larger image)" alt="Maple Snell, the Friday Cat (click for larger image)" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3416/3259668702_0c12c9331b_b.jpg" width="640" height="427"></a> </p> <p>From January 9, 2009, a glimpse of Maple sitting among the humans at a small dinner among friends.&nbsp;&nbsp; Maple may not be too sure about the photographer, here, although the cat seems quite at home among the crowd at one of the Snell’s annual holiday parties.</p>  <div style="clear:both; padding-bottom:0.25em"></div><p class="blogger-labels">Labels: <a rel='tag' href="http://orcmid.com/blog/labels/cats.asp">cats</a>, <a rel='tag' href="http://orcmid.com/blog/labels/friends and family.asp">friends and family</a></p>
    </p>
	<span class="byline">posted by orcmid 
       at <a href="http://orcmid.com/blog/2009/02/friday-cat-photo-maple-snell.asp">2/06/2009 07:40:00 PM</a></span>
	  
